      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty ride and it's looking for a brand new home! This car has been so good to me\u2014it's in really solid shape, super reliable, and honestly just a joy to drive. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-taken care of, so it's ready to hit the road with you today. If you're looking for a dependable car that still has tons of life left in it, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 28900.0,
